    "arv5:83": "vāyu-dhātuś-ca ||",
    "arv5:84": "Pṛthivī-dhātuḥ katamaḥ?",
    "arv5:85": "Yad gurutvaṁ kakkhaṭatvaṁ ca ||",
    "arv5:86": "Ab-dhātuḥ katamaḥ?",
    "arv5:87": "Yad dravatvam-abhiṣyandanatvaṁ ca ||",
    "arv5:88": "Tejo-dhātuḥ katamaḥ?",
    "arv5:89": "Yad-uṣṇatvaṁ ca paripācanatvaṁ ca ||",
    "arv5:90": "Vāyu-dhātuḥ katamaḥ?",
    "arv5:91": "Yad-ākuñcana-prasāraṇa-laghu-samudīraṇatvaṁ ca ||",
    "arv5:92": "Yad-idaṁ rūpaṁ pūrvakaṁ ca nāma ||",
    "arv5:93": "Tad-ubhayam-ekatrābhisaṁkṣipya nāma-rūpam-ity-ucyate ||",
