    "arv5:211": "Ākāśānantyāyatanaṁ |",
    "arv5:212": "Vijñānānantyāyatanaṁ |",
    "arv5:213": "Ākiṁcanyāyatanaṁ |",
    "arv5:214": "Naivasaṁjñā-nāsaṁjñāyatanam ||",
    "arv5:215": "Ārūpiṇāṁ devānāṁ citta-mātra-dhyāyināṁ cātur-vidhopapattiḥ ||",
